<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Admin Panel</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">DbD Bundles - Admin</div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Početna</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">O Igri / Projektu</a></li>
                <li><a href="/kontakt">Kontakt</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admin">Admin panel</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h1>Pregled pristiglih poruka iz baze</h1>
        <p>Ova stranica je dostupna samo administratorima i vuče sve kontakt poruke upisane preko POST metode.</p>

        <div class="table-container">
            <% if (poruke.length === 0) { %>
                <p style="color: #ff4444; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 20px;">Trenutno nema nijedne poruke u bazi.</p>
            <% } else { %>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>ID</th>
                            <th>Ime pošiljaoca</th>
                            <th>Email</th>
                            <th>Sadržaj Poruke</th>
                            <th>Datum primanja</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% poruke.forEach(poruka => { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td><%= poruka.id %></td>
                                <td><strong><%= poruka.ime %></strong></td>
                                <td><a href="mailto:<%= poruka.email %>" style="color:#ff4444;"><%= poruka.email %></a></td>
                                <td><%= poruka.poruka %></td>
                                <td><%= new Date(poruka.datum).toLocaleString('sr-RS') %></td>
                            </tr>
                        <% }); %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Dead by Daylight Prodaja Bundlova - Node.js Projekat</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>